WEBVTT FILE:

00:00:00.850 --> 00:00:05.560
The most important first step that I can think of is to get to know your

00:00:05.560 --> 00:00:10.270
 people. That goes a long way to establishing trust, asking them how

00:00:10.270 --> 00:00:14.970
 they are, where they're from, what they're doing, not necessarily

00:00:14.970 --> 00:00:19.680
 in detail, but just figuring out a little bit about them. Once you

00:00:19.680 --> 00:00:24.390
 have some sort of personal connection to somebody, not only does it

00:00:24.390 --> 00:00:29.100
 does it, you establish a report, but it personalizes the leader. You

00:00:29.100 --> 00:00:33.800
 know it, it makes him It shows that they are human. And they're not

00:00:33.800 --> 00:00:38.510
 just this This person that is under that is untouchable by subordinates

00:00:38.510 --> 00:00:43.220
 below.

